n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8D%8E%E4%B8%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%258D%258E%25E4%25B8%25BA&d=FOSiJIdA3EVv5kz%2FnXbgJQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=591bde98\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8D%8E%E4%B8%BA</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">華為技術公司是中華人民共和國一家從事資訊與通訊解決方案的供應商，總部位於廣東省深圳市。</span>華為於1987年註冊成立，業務範圍涉及電信網路、企業網路、消費者和雲端運算。其電信網路產品主要包括通訊網路中的交換網路、傳輸網路、無線及有線固定接入網路和資料通訊網路及無線終端產品。 <br />\n總部： 中國深圳市<br />\n創立於： 1987 年，中國深圳市"},{"pid":"fa96d957d7e1c4a5a3bb30327fc0e6df9062a2c2","tid":90014,"uid":1187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T08:21:01.000Z","msg":"Csl 7月完求smt sales<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e842805afc02a0c5c89581ca6ba5c066a5ad53a","tid":90014,"uid":1187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T08:24:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Csl 7月完求smt sales<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n補返contact telegram: tomhk2017<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47125143c0209567d081dc0eeb6fe852fcf244f5","tid":90014,"uid":76360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:51:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}